{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC01_WIL_610.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x17,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "*sigh* Nothing exciting ever happens these days..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Bell, you seem pretty down today."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. I still haven't decided on my task for Great-great-grandmother."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Being able to do whatever you want is so troublesome. It would've been better if I just had to cast a spell 1,000 times."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "It must be hard, not knowing what to do. What've you done so far that didn't work out?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x169,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Well, saving a village that was possessed by a demon, writing a book report on an ancient magic book..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x16b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "And I even kept an observation journal while growing man-eating plants from the underworld."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Whoa, you've done a bunch of different things..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x165,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "I've done a looot more, but I'm running out of ideas..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x166,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Now do you see why I turned to others for help?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x167,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "On top of that, I have my daily training, and it's not that easy to cover my living expenses, either."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Uh-huh, it's tough to earn money."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3f,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "So, getting fed whenever I come here really helps. And it's always delicious!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x34,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Hehe, no problem."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x41,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Ugh, if only I didn't have to worry<CR>about money. I just wanna make some<CR>big money and focus on my training."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Well, people say haste makes waste, so if you work hard and steadily, I'm sure you'll save up some money naturally."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Well, I'm not really the \"work hard and steadily\" kind of person..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "I wanna be like, kaboom!<CR>Hit the jackpot!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Anyway, for now, I'll do as you say, haste makes waste, to hit the jackpot!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0xc4,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "I feel like you're contradicting yourself..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "Alright! Now that it's decided,<CR>I just gotta do it!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x19a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "See ya!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x36,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Bell... She's just so...Bell. Hehehe!"
        }
    ]
}